CREATE YOUR OWN! - or - GET PAID TO TAKE SURVEYS!

I dream of floating fireflys and
Monkeys on the sea
I think of sandy waterfalls and 
Dancing on a scree
I'd like to play and somersalt
Above the oceans front
And sit on little elephants and
laugh and cry and grunt

I want to have a tangerine
That tastes of melon dew
Where big fat worms do gobble goop and
Drink salamander Stew
I want a piglets curly fries
And a green flamingos beak
And bath upon the seasons edge
For answers I might seek

I want to buy a walrus so 
His head is not too fat
And train a tiny porcupine to
Lay upon my mat.
The day of stealing Noahs boat
Cannot come any sooner
But for now I'm quite content
Just playing with my Luna.

argh. appologies to the ppl i have seemed evil with lately. im mega stressed and acting it. just feel really despondant and sad and worried...basically im doing what i always do at exam time and think im a failure who doesnt know shit. i always end up doing ace but i cant get my head around that before exams. i felt so ANGRY today. grrrrr. so i went for a run and it really helped, i think i must have been making angry faces tho because ppl made gave me a wide birth to pass them n the street. a week left of this horridness and itll be over...then its time to start my festivals, drinking and chilling....come on week, ill eat you for breakfast!

need to run, get that blood pumping...or i could just have lots of the secksi time. i prefer that option. oh ye and i decided to go to chicago for the lollapalooza fectival and then go see freddie for a bit....woot. if i can afford it. arrgh. or mayeb its the delerium talking. maybe i should book tickets AFTER exams. yes. i think so.

Well i think i might just have to stop having so much fun now.... uni started again and i actually have....EXAMS! shitzer. at least i used the holiday to get 2 essays done which im proud of because most of the days has been a blur of sex drugs and rock and roll....woot. but nah i have to settle down now, calm yourself Iago! right now im confused..but happy...confappy? i guess u dont know when somethings gonna sneak up behind u and go 'ba! lalalala you dont know what to dooo lalalalalala' im torn like a torn monkey called maurice.
Watched Dylan Moran yesterday, fucking hilarious...had quite a good night of comedy at the Beefs actually...and got pretty high too, good conbination! but as i said i have to start living in the real world again. Boo!
I can get 10 ppl into Jillys free on the night of 20th or 21st before 10:30 so whoever wants in let me know...meep.

I have taken a vow of silence in my house. Mainly because if i talk anymore the razor blades in my thoat threaten to cut right through....
Second because i think people think i talk to much, and that sometimes makes me look shallow.
Thirdly because i think even though i like to assume i listen alot i think i could listen more.,....so we'll see how this goes.
Im not going to go into the events of this weekend because it makes me tired just thinking about it.....so urll have to guess. ha. I went into work today and was told to go home because i probably looked like shit and cetainly sounded like shit. Should i do this more often?

I am becoming a bum. I have only been to 1 lecture this week, done absolutely no work, have been out every night and havnt done my washing up for a week. What the hell is wrong with me, this is very out of character. Cock was down for the week which is the reason i did no work but i have no excuse for the rest of my lack in hygiene and complete laziness. I havnt been running for nearly a week and drinking too much beer, thus developing a pot...this wont do. I need a kick up the ass, and a shower.
However yesterdays fun and games was great. Went to Rockworld with Phil, Sandrine and Scott and didnt even drink much as i was sort of still hungover from the night before. There was a very good looking boy on the dancefloor who kept suprisingly popping up every now and again (coincidence?) but as i was stone sober even his good looks didnt sway me and i didnt bother to seem interested. i got home in one piece but didnt get to sleep till at least 4, thanks to phil and sandrine!! its ok i forgive u. so ye my days have all blended into one big wierd lump lately, and im thoughroughly (sp?) enjoying it.

boooya mofos. Ahhh crazyness dawned on me yesterday. i am suffering the effects though. Went out for a meal with Liz, cock and sandrine was tres good then went to Phils and got wasted. When i say wasted i mean waaaaaaaassssted, so WASTED in fact i cant remember half the night. But i had a lot of fun. It all went downhill when phil made me take a jack hammer (tequila and jack) and then about half a bottle of baileys. Achhh. I had work at 9 this morning, oh my god if it wasnt for Luke who kept giving me hugs to keep me going i think i would have died. Took cock up to the station and now im in my pjs again. I cant belive im going out tonight aswell, im such a tard. I do rather like these new friends im making, much more my kinda people, crazy people!!! i have a bruised eye and cheekbone and i dont know what from, i dont recall falling on my FACE. ah well it alls comes with being young and foolish. An old lady told me she really liked my green hair today in the shop and that she wanted to dye hers pink, shes my idol. she was buying crickets so i think she even has a snake, go old lady, rararara.
ya! 
Do it!!

p.s what the fuck was with all the couples yesterday, i was walking on the street in the middle of town and this couple stopped right in front of me to kiss, i had to walk around then, i was nearly sick. fucking hallmark

To all that can, come to satans tomoro!! good ya!

I have to say this weekend was mightily awesome. Friday was Jollyes staff pub crawl and i must say i had an amazing time. It was so nice to see Dave again. Like I forgot what it was like to speak to a genuine person who you admire and who is good looking but with no sexual attraction there whatsoever. Its liberating i tell you. So ye talked to Dave most the night, just needed to talk to someone who doesnt put on a face for ppl and is actually themselves. Sandrine was hilarious, i love her to bits. Anyway so ye started off in the Didsbury followed by Old Cock and them myself, Dave, Sandrine and Chrys went to Fab...where i migth add i only drank water! I figured if i drank more id have a banging headache the next day. Look at me, im getting sensible.
But ye rest of weekend was good on a few aspects. I added an extra 20 minutes to my run, and felt good about it! Me and Chris are on speaking terms again, which is great! All ive eaten is chicken stir fry, not necessarily a bad thing, chicken stir fry rockz my sockz. And ye lazed around, been to blockbuster...watched the Big lebowski and Almost Famous, two rather brilliant movies. And actually did some uni work.
So ye theres my weekend in a nut chell. Oh and Sandrine is coming to Italy with me this easter...yay!

I officially hair green hair...well the tips really but like 2 or 3 inchs at bottom...i think its rather funky. Always wanted the green but was scared id look like a cabbage...but alas its a wierd turquoisy oceany green so cant be mistaken for a fruit or vegetable. pics to come!

So.... 
Yesterday was alright. I dunno....felt like something was missing. I dont feel greatly satisfied. Today has been a lazy day, went to Trof for lunch and just been dozing this afternoon. Im having a horrible anti climax type feeling, like blah, i dunno! Some people can be very hurtful. A few important people in my life havnt bothered contacting me which makes me a little sad. Also being single isnt all that fun at times...no responsability but i miss being the most important person to somebody.  
Anyway this is a depressing post! i guess getting older makes you think a little about things, looking at your life so far and wanding if ur happy with it. Im very happy with my life but there are always those days where u feel like telling the world to go screw itself. 
Go screw yourself.
Its funny how you build up somebody or something in your mind to be good and then it turns out their not all their cracked up to be and you wonder why you really worried about it. I think from now on I'll spend more time worrying about important things and concentrating on my work.
Ive eaten too many quality street today...just munching through them watching deal or no deal.

bamjsnshsdhdsjkdh!!!
Ah! Amazing. I am having the most amazing 48hrs with Sally! We were gonna go for a 'quiet drink' yesterday which ended up grand central and 5th Ave where we met some random crazy people and took them home, muahahaha. One of them was Jazzy Jeff...well not literally but he was HILARIOUS. Today we went to see a movie and we're going t Jillys later...and i have work tomoro! woot. This is the life. Im knacked but i feel great!

Soooo ye. Evening has been a waste. got ready to do something then ended up waiting about, again. alas. But! looky looky at scaffold! The bar is MASSIVE but thats just to allow swelling, ill get a shorter bar once its healed.

I did quite alot today. worked in the morning, went for a run. Then went into town and got a scaffold piercing, its pretty damn fly. Was gonna go see perfume but i ended up having no one to see it with *violins playing in the background* so ye....also was gonna go out tonight but corronation street is on and im a loser. fingers crossed tomoro will prove fruitful. Pics of the piercing yet to come!
oh ye and i could kick ur ass. yes, you.

So exams are all done. what an anticlimax. I did some food shoping, came home and spring cleaned my room...i feel fulfilled...but not. 
I have no one to party with as people still have exams left and have no one to party with the rest of the week because they all have better things to do! Mother is coming this weekend. Christ. Should be fun though, shes taking me out for my bday...a week early. Cocks prob coming down with sean for my bday though so thats a yay point.
So yeeeeeeeee. feel kinda despondant for some reason. It could be the crack.

Im happy. I seriously dont give a fuck about the shitty things right now! i mean i have exams that i havnt revised for on monday and tuesday.....work is, well work, i cant really avoid the dog piss. boys....HA! good one. i dont really care, im not gonna really look for anything, ill see what comes my way instead, im not exactly desperate anyway right now. Sally is a godsend....fred, she reminds me of u. and my house is alright right now. Thank god liz is here to buffer everything! im not that healthy right now but im doing alright. 
so ye even tho everything is so so im not sad...im actually happy. 

I wanna go somewhere soon...like randomly, i might just go to the station and get on a train....

Well ive finally gotten over my two day hangover and find myself alone and bored. I may as well have also just fucked up the only good thing going for me in my life. Exams are next week and i havnt started the mega huge essay i have to give in next monday. I have work all next week so i dont where i will find the time. None of my housemates are here excpet my ex who happens to be at his gilrfriends house all the time. Thanks god for sally and introducing me to 'what a wonderful world' ramones version.
When it rains it pours.....

p.s Freddddddie i need ye

Well what an odd week or so it has been. I love my friends so much here but i cant help but feel that Manchester is now my home. I just feel so much more I dunno....myself? no...happy? i guess....whatever it is I cant wait to go back. I have exams and essays and work waiting for me but who cares after a few weeks itll all be over and i can celebrate my bday, in style might i add! I have no clue what to do though, any ideas? Im saving pulling out the big guns till my 21st so nothing too drastic. I want people from work, friends at uni, outside uni ect all to be there so itll have to be something everyone can do...so no studenty places.
hmmmm...
So new years eh. Do i have any resolutions...I dont think so. I dont because they never work. I never keep them anyway, i dont have much will power. 
Right well im ready for a night of craziness and who knows what will happen!

Well Well Welllllll
Lookie whos writing in her LJ. Indulge me LJ! I went fucking nuts today. I cycled shag loads through the forest then i took a bath with champagne and put on some really expensive cloths and swaned around for bout an hour then changed into my pj's for the rest of the day. I didnt stop drinking, i ate far too much and now i kinda feel odd. Well there is an asnwer to it all....its Christmas! lala. Well finally, fuck, i havnt felt in the spirit all bloody month and i get it on the day, woowee. 
Ive had a shitty month, very very shitty. The only positive thing/s are that i met an uber (I swore id never use that word again) cool boy who shall not be named and im seeing micky/cock/lawrence/eug/albi/sean/etc etc again for the first time in fuckin ages!
Well yep. This shitty stuff is everything with chris and those who know me prob know anyway. Well i hope he and her have a wonderful time together. Whatthefuckever eh? Well finally we can be friends which is the good thing right?
Anyway I did meet a nice boy :) and im telling anymore muahahaha...its just nice and bloody refreshing you know? after so long of feeling so rejected and fed up and hurt its just nice to chill out with someone and have a laugh and stuff...yep.
So ye I ate lots. Ive not been able to eat all week then Christmas day hits me and its like BAM EAT ME. and i did. And i feel like i dont need to eat anythign else for a week.
So yes
This is it
Over and out
Merry Christmas Homies

HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU, HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU, HAPPY BIRTHDAY DEAR FREDMEISTER HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO YOU.

Fred, I can't believe its your bday already, your getting old. I remember you getting mad when you turned 19 thinking you were so old....
lol but i bet its nice now your at the age of ultimate youth mixed with maturity...basically you can do what the fuck you like and have an excuse for it.

Montreal was fucking amaizng. I partied, got pissed and pierced. Amazing.

wow so i dont know where to start. Im writing this in a little room in camp robindel new hamsphire! It was really sad leaving all my friends in uni and even worse leaving chris but finally got to airport and found out my virgin flight had been cancelled and i have to take an air india instead :O it wasnt very good, stewerdesses did shit all, my screen was broken and at the start pf the flight the oxygen masks acidentally fell out lol. Anyway i arrived alive thank god in JFK airport and we took a bus to the hostel. Id met some really cool ppl on flight so we went into new york, time square and ooohed and ahhhed at all the pretty lights and ate steak. Was good. Next day all by my lonesome i took bus to boston and then to new hampshire and was picked up at a little gad station with another girl to be taken to the camp. So ive already had my 3 day intensive ropes course, soooo much fun. Did all kinds of cool stuff, zip line into lake, maddive swing, etc. and i also passed my test to be an instuctor so yay! 
Orientation for staff starts this evening and im kinds tired coz me and friends stayed up playing texas hold em for a while which by the way i had the most chips in OH YE!
Chris left for pennsylvania this morning so i wont be able to talk to him for a while, hope hes ok. 
phew its been a strange week indeed but very good. lonely at times and fun others but all over i think im gonna have a great summer. 
And fred, ill be calling you any day now just need to by some phone cards xx
